                                   CHANGES

                                DBWatcher(TM) 3
                                Version 3.0.0.0
	
r3-0-2-0	cmyun	2011-08-10	
			* 전체색인을 제외한 색인시 (추가/필드업데이트 등) .ini.old 와 .sql.old 를 사용하도록 수정. (old 가 없을 시에는 기존 .ini 와 .sql 을 사용)
			cresearch	2011-01-21
			* Fix skipping sending an email report when an exception throws
			* Fix throwing an exception corresponding to flag 'useFileWrite' of 'TRANSMIT_PROTOCOL = FILE'

r3-0-1-4	dggim	2009-07-22                            
			* Support 'Altibase 4.x'
			* Support 'Altibase 5.x'

r3-0-1-3	shlee	2008-05-27
	* Add 'NULLABLE' property
		- Map parameters might contain null values for the following functions:
			- com.diquest.dbwatcher.ext.DbExtension#getColumn(String, Map)
			- com.diquest.dbwatcher.ext.DbExtension#getUpdateID(Map)
			- com.diquest.dbwatcher.ext.DbExtension#getID(Map)
			- com.diquest.dbwatcher.ext.DbExtension#validData(Map)
		- Columns composing DOC_ID, CHANGE_DOC_ID cannot have null value any more.

r3-0-1-2	shlee	2008-05-21
	* Fix logging in a fail log when validDate method returns false
	* Add logging followings in a success log(with INFO category in DEBUG_MODE)
		- Database Product Name
		- Database Product Version
		- Driver Name
		- Driver Version

r3-0-1-1	shlee	2008-03-18
	* Fix problem invoking method using java.lang.reflect

r3-0-1-0	shlee	2008-03-10
	* Add Shutdown functionality
		* Add a new argument to listen shutdown request for DbWatcher
			ex) java -cp ... ...DbWatcher ... --port 4885 ...
		* Request DbWatcher shutdown
			java -cp DBWatcher.jar com.diquest.dbwatcher.command.Shutdown IP:PORT
			ex) java -cp ... ...Shutdown 127.0.0.1:4885

r3-0-0-2	shlee	2008-01-09
	* Fix DBExtension, 2.X DBExtension binary compatible
	* Fix, errors in a thread make other threads stop correctly
	* Fix errata example of INDEX_DATA in file sample.ini, DBWatcher.ini

r3-0-0-1	shlee	2007-12-20
	* Fix INDEX_DATA to be capitalized (like 2.X)
	* Fix lines in configuration files to be trimmed (like 2.X)

r3-0-0-0	shlee	2007-12-11
	* Support multi-threaded collecting
	* Support 'PostgreSQL'
	* Support 'CUBRID'
	* Support recording collected information
	* Add early error detecting methods
	* Add 'REPLACE_SPECIAL' property
	* Add 'DB_ENCODING' property
	* Change default package classes to named package
		- com.diquest.dbwatcher.ext.DbExtension (replace DBExtension)
		- com.diquest.dbwatcher.DbWatcher (replace DBWatcher)
		- com.diquest.dbwatcher.DbBridge (replace DBBridge)
		- com.diquest.dbwatcher.command.CommandWrapper (replace CommandWrapper)
	* Add informative MANIFEST in jar
	* Fix reading escape space ('\ ') incorrectly
	* Fix trimming the value of configuration file

r2-6-2	shlee	2007-07-03
	* Add 'USE_COLUMN_LABEL' property
	* Add 'MYSQL5' for 'DRIVER_TYPE' property
	* Add 'MYSQL5_STREAM' for 'DRIVER_TYPE' property

r2-6-1	shlee	2007-04-30
	* Add 'CUSTOM' for 'DRIVER_TYPE' property
	* Add 'DRIVER_CLASS' property

r2-6-0	shlee	2007-01-18
	* Support timeout
	* Fix applying INSERT_FILE_SIZE can cause integer overflow
	* Fix writing delete file didn't apply encoding

r2-5-2	shlee	2006-11-22
	* Fix unsupported setFetchSize problem in i-net(SQL Server) driver
	* Fix duplicated new line characters

r2-5-1	shlee	2006-11-15
	* Add sqljdbc.jar
	* Add 'SQLJDBC' for 'DRIVER_TYPE'

r2-5-0	omegatribe	2006-07-14
    * Change mysql.jar to version 3.1.13
	* Fix NullPointerException relate to logging.

r2-4-0	omegatribe	2006-03-10
	* Add 'INSERT_FILE_SIZE' property
	* Add 'ENCODING' property

r2-3-5	omegatribe	2006-02-13
	* Support fetch size

r2-3-4	panda005	2004-12-10
	* Support 'DQIR 2.3' style 'indexd.status'
	* Add 'WRITE_INDEX_STATUS' property
	* Add 'SERVER_ENDIAN' property

r2-3-3	panda005	2004-12-10
	* Add 'USE_JDBC_URL' property
	* Add 'JDBC_URL' property
	* Change binary to be compatible with JRE 1.3

r2-3-2	panda005	2004-10-18
	* Add db2java.zip
	* Add db2jcc.jar

r2-3-1	panda005	2004-10-12
	* Support reading escape sequence in configuration file
	* Change character '' to ' '

r2-3-0	cyllian	2003-09-05
	* Support SQL Server MS949
	* Support binary stream

r2-2-0	cyllian	2003-03-17
	* Support INFORMIX
	* Support SYBASE
	* Add 'INSERT_UPDATE_QUERY' property sequence start from 1
	* Add 'CLEAN_UPDATE_QUERY' property sequence start from 1

r2-1-0	cyllian	2002-12-28
	* Support IBM AS/400
	* Support UniSQL
	* Add 'DB_PORTNUM' property
	* Add 'TRANSMIT_PROCOTOL' property
	* Add 'TRANSMIT_INSERT_FILENAME' property
	* Add 'TRANSMIT_DELETE_FILENAME' property
	* Add 'TRANSMIT_HOSTNAME' property	(deprecated 'HOSTNAME')
	* Add 'TRANSMIT_PORTNUM' property	(deprecated 'PORTNUM')
	* Add 'TRANSMIT_TIMEOUT' property	(deprecated 'TIMEOUT')
	* Add 'PROGRESS' for 'DEBUG_MODE'
	* Add a method 'String getPrefix()' in 'DBBridge' class
	* Change SQL Server JDBC Driver
	* Change SQL Server default fetch size to 1024
	* Fix sending idxlsnr deleted information via delaying
	* Fix parsing prefix argument incorrectly

r2-0-0	cyllian	2002-09-15
	* Renew collect schemes

r1-1-3	cyllian	2002-03-21
	* Support MySQL

r1-1-2	cyllian	2002-03-07
	* Support idxlsnr for DQIR 2.0
	* Add a function for supporting DQIR administration tool
	* Fix bugs relate to KSC5601

r1-1-1	cyllian 2001-05-22
	* Support TNS setting for ORACLE DBMS
	* Add an option for collecting via an event table
	* Fix bugs for SQL Server dependent

r1-1-0	cyllian	2001-04-17
	* Support ID-value
	* Add 'CUSTOM_CLASS' property
	* Fix bugs for ORACLE DBMS dependent

r1-0-0	cyllian	2001-03-08
	* The first release

